# Typed pattern implementation

```scalascript
case class IndentContext(currentLevel: Int)

def level(value: Any): Int = value match
  case context: Wrapper[IndentContext] => context.currentLevel

def classify(value: Any): String = value match
  case context: Wrapper[(IndentContext, List[Int])] if context.currentLevel > 1 => "deep"
  case context: Wrapper[(IndentContext, List[Int])]                             => "shallow"
```
